back\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 23, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nti1665703546274.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nti1665703546274.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nti1665703546274.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nti1665703546274\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"nti1665703546274__assignment_setting_1967\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A configuration definition in an assignment file that determines one aspect of a Uniface application's environment or behavior. Assignment settings can define the location of application resources and log files, application logicals, the default language and library, default properties of widgets, and system settings that influence the runtime behavior.\n </p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nti1665703546274__li_d2e1_d3e1_d4e1\">Sets environment variables for the development, testing and\n            production of the application.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nti1665703546274__li_d5e1_d6e1_d7e1\">Specifies the language to be used for messages and help\n            texts.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nti1665703546274__li_d8e1_d9e1_d10e1\">Specifies the keyboard translation table and device translation\n            table to be used.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nti1665703546274__li_d11e1_d12e1_d13e1\">Defines the location of DBMS tables referenced by the\n            application.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nti1665703546274__li_d14e1_d15e1_d16e1\">Defines a logical name that can be accessed with the $logical\n            ProcScript function.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nti1665703546274__li_d17e1_d18e1_d19e1\">Defines the location of non-DBMS files accessed by an\n            application and specifies where components are executed.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nti1665703546274__li_d20e1_d21e1_d22e1\">Defines any Uniface system setting, to influence run-time\n            behavior.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530420\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530420\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "assignment setting Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 23, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 A configuration definition in an assignment file that determines one aspect of a Uniface application's environment or behavior. Assignment settings can define the location of application resources and log files, application logicals, the default language and library, default properties of widgets, and system settings that influence the runtime behavior. Sets environment variables for the development, testing and production of the application. Specifies the language to be used for messages and help texts. Specifies the keyboard translation table and device translation table to be used. Defines the location of DBMS tables referenced by the application. Defines a logical name that can be accessed with the $logical ProcScript function. Defines the location of non-DBMS files accessed by an application and specifies where components are executed. Defines any Uniface system setting, to influence run-time behavior. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}